From 7ca8b47acce676006a56e729ce86bf4a9aec4937 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sat, 28 Feb 2026 16:17:05 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add Birthday Bucket as standalone tool integrated into main
 UI

Integrates ChurchSuite birthday functionality as a separate tool (like
Service Generator), accessible via a header button when enabled in settings.

New files:
- src/types/churchsuite.ts - ChurchSuiteConfig, BirthdayPerson, BirthdayEntry types
- src/services/churchsuite-client.ts - ChurchSuite API HTTP client with pagination
- src/services/churchsuite-contacts.ts - Fetch contacts with birthdays
- src/services/churchsuite-children.ts - Fetch children with birthdays
- src/services/birthday.ts - Week birthday calculation, filtering, and sorting
- src/services/birthday-pptx.ts - PowerPoint slide generation for birthdays
- electron/renderer/src/BirthdayBucketView.tsx - Full Birthday Bucket view component

Modified files:
- electron/renderer/src/App.tsx - Added birthdayBucket mode, header button, settings toggle
- electron/preload/index.ts - Added ChurchSuite IPC bridge methods
- electron/main/index.ts - Added ChurchSuite IPC handlers (sync, getBirthdays, exportPptx)

https://claude.ai/code/session_01WPfoRHHhbdcJhigeof3L3K
